{"word":"ταγεύω","slug":"ταγεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ταγεύω</b></el> <el>(τᾱγεύω,) ( φυτ. <el>-σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ταγός'><el>ταγός</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be Chief</i> of Thessaly, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be united under one</i> <el>ταγός</el>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to let</i> soldiers <i>be posted</i> or <i>stationed</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}